parameters:
Karin-chan, are you going out? If you need me, please take
me with you. I'm sure I can be of help.
...(It's noisy... I wonder if something happened.)
Momiji-san, are you there!? It's terrible!

I'm sorry, but on the main street of the pleasure district,
some drunk samurai retainers are causing a ruckus! Can you
stop them?
Heh heh heh♪ What's wrong with doing it right here? Let us!

Ahh! Violence and disorder are strictly forbidden in the
pleasure district! If you want to do it, pay and go inside a
mansion...!

Hah! Putting on airs! We are samurai retainers, you know!
You courtesans have no right to order us around!
That's enough. Please let go of that woman.
Hehehe! That bobbed haircut, are you bald or something?

We're so turned on we can't calm down! If you don't want to
get hit, scram!

I am a geisha of this pleasure district... as well as a
bouncer. If you don't want to get hurt, leave this district
immediately.

Uwahaha! A bouncer, huh? That's hilarious! You're the one
who's gonna get hurt!

We don't show mercy to anyone who opposes us! This is what
happens to those who get in our way!
Gyaaa!? My arm...! My arm's gonna break~~!!?

--!? Ahh! What are you doing!? Just grab her by the chest
and pin her down, that'll settle it!

Ouchhh! Eeeeek~~~!! (Idiot!? How can such a little girl have
such ridiculous strength--!? )

...If I do any more, your arm will snap. Do you want to end
up with a broken arm and hospitalized?

Eeeek!? I understand! We were wrong! Please forgive us! If
you keep holding our arms like that, they'll break!

Sorry! We won't mess with the courtesans anymore! We just
got carried away with the drink and caused a scene! P-Please
forgive us! Eeeeek~~~!!!
No. Thank you for your help, Momiji-san.

My my, your strength is always so impressive. Here's a
little something for your trouble. Keep it.

(Master, it's been half a year since you've returned... I
wonder where on earth you could be...)
Oh! Momiji! It's been a while!

--! Master!? I've been searching for you all this time?
Where have you been until now?

My apologies, my apologies. There were various
circumstances. I was attacked by demons and lost my mystical
energy, reverting back to my fox form. Then I was captured
by humans... It's been quite a difficult time.
...(Ugh... he smells like an unwashed dog...)
Oof! My back is so itchy... Could you scratch it for me?

These are ticks, you know? You need to take a bath
quickly... I'll go fill the barrel with hot water right now.

(--That girl, her name was Karin, wasn't it. She took good
care of me. I must repay her kindness someday...)
